(116, '{\"en\": \"sai-medical-clinic-for-children-venezuela\", \"es\": \"sai-abre-una-nueva-clínica-ambulatoria-en-venezuela\"}', '{\"en\": \"SAI Medical Clinic for Children - Venezuela\", \"es\": \"SAI abre una Nueva Clínica Ambulatoria en Venezuela\"}', '{\"en\": \"SAI Children’s Medical Clinic\", \"es\": \"<h2 class=\\\"MsoNoSpacing\\\" style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><strong>Resumen</strong></h2>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNoSpacing\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.6px;\\\">Las estad&iacute;sticas econ&oacute;micas actuales estiman que el 90% de los venezolanos est&aacute;n viviendo en pobreza. Esto est&aacute; afectando a todos, pero en especial a los ni&ntilde;os. Cuando los ni&ntilde;os van a la cama con hambre, se despiertan a&uacute;n m&aacute;s hambrientos y cuando los ni&ntilde;os no reciben la atenci&oacute;n m&eacute;dica y los medicamentos adecuados, los problemas de salud comunes pueden convertirse en toda una vida de condiciones graves. Esa es la raz&oacute;n por la que Iniciativa Sudamericana tiene la misi&oacute;n de salvar a los ni&ntilde;os de Venezuela, entregando alimentos y brindando atenci&oacute;n m&eacute;dica.</span></p>\"}', '{\"en\": \"<iframe  loading=\\\"lazy\\\"  allowpaymentrequest=\\\"\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" height=\\\"900px\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/sai-children-s-medical-clinic\\\" style=\\\" height: 1429px; max-height: none !important;\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" data-donorbox-id=\\\"DonorBox-f1\\\"></iframe>\", \"es\": \"<iframe class=\\\"ifrimi\\\" src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/helpvenezuela-us?only_donation_meter=true&amp;donation_meter_color=%232ecc71\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\"    max-height: 93px !important;     height: 92px;\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" data-donorbox-id=\\\"DonorBox-f1\\\"></iframe><iframe class=\\\"aframa\\\" id=\\\"ifrimi\\\" src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/helpvenezuela-us?hide_donation_meter=true\\\" height=\\\"685px\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\" max-height: none !important; height: 1204px;\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" allowpaymentrequest=\\\"\\\" data-donorbox-id=\\\"DonorBox-f2\\\"></iframe>\"}', '{\"en\": \"<iframe width=\\\"560\\\" height=\\\"315\\\" src=\\\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nydUXKJY7Uk\\\" title=\\\"YouTube video player\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allow=\\\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\\\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\", \"es\": \"<iframe width=\\\"560\\\" height=\\\"315\\\" src=\\\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nydUXKJY7Uk\\\" title=\\\"YouTube video player\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allow=\\\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\\\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\"}', '{\"en\": {\"special_tag\": \"Urgent Help\", \"description_heading\": \"Description Heading\", \"description_text\": \"Detailed Description\", \"summary_title\": \"Summary\", \"summary_text\": \"Current economic statistics estimate that 90% of Venezuelans are now living in poverty. This is taking a huge toll on everyone -- but most noticeably, the children. When kids go to bed hungry, they wake up even hungrier. When children don\'t get the proper medical care and medicine, common health problems can turn into a lifetime of serious health conditions. That\'s the reason South American Initiative is on a mission to save the children of Venezuela. We do this with meals and medical care.\", \"help_mini_title\": \"Help People In need\", \"help_title\": \"Start Donating Today, Make The Difference\", \"help_btn_text\": \"DONATE TO THIS PROJECT >\"}, \"es\": {\"special_tag\": \"Ayuda urgente\", \"description_heading\": \"Subtitulo por defecto\", \"description_text\": \"Texto de descripción por defecto\", \"summary_title\": \"Resumen\", \"summary_text\": \"Current economic statistics estimate that 90% of Venezuelans are now living in poverty. This is taking a huge toll on everyone -- but most noticeably, the children. When kids go to bed hungry, they wake up even hungrier. When children don\'t get the proper medical care and medicine, common health problems can turn into a lifetime of serious health conditions. That\'s the reason South American Initiative is on a mission to save the children of Venezuela. We do this with meals and medical care.\", \"help_mini_title\": \"Ayuda a personas en necesidad\", \"help_title\": \"Comienza a donar hoy, Haz la diferencia\", \"help_btn_text\": \"DONAR A ESTE PROYECTO >\"}}', '{\"en\": \"<h2>Challenge</h2>\\n<p>In Venezuela the national healthcare system has failed. Most of the doctors and nurses have left the country due to political unrest and skyrocketing inflation. Hospitals are dilapidated and run down with frequent power outages, contaminated drinking water, no air conditioning, and patients lie in dirty bedding with no clean sheets.</p>\\n<h2>Solution</h2>\\n<p>Our medical clinic provides medical care and medicine to those children in need. This includes orphans and homeless children who need medical care for open wounds, gastrointestinal problems from eating rotten food and dirty drinking water and providing essential medication.</p>\\n<h2>Long-Term Impact</h2>\\n<p>This project will benefit local children who cannot get proper care at their local hospitals and need immediate medical attention. For many children, our clinic is their only option when they are in need of urgent medical care.</p>\", \"es\": \"<h2>Desafío</h2>\\n<p>En Venezuela el sistema nacional de salud ha fallado. La mayoría de los doctores y enfermeras han dejado el país debido a los disturbios políticos e inflación vertiginosa.</p>\\n<h2>Solución</h2>\\n<p>Nuestro consultorio médico brinda atención médica y medicinas a los niños que más lo necesitan.</p>\\n<h2>Impacto a Largo Tiempo</h2>\\n<p>Este proyecto beneficiará a niños de la comunidad local quienes no puedan recibir la atención médica adecuada e inmediata en hospitales locales.</p>\"}', '{\"en\": null, \"es\": \"\"}', '{}', 'published\r\n', NULL, 1, '2025-07-21 17:32:11', '2025-07-21 17:32:11'),
(117, '{\"en\": \"help-venezuelan-hospitals-supplying-food-and-medicine\", \"es\": \"hospitales\"}', '{\"en\": \"Help Venezuelan Hospitals | Supplying Food and Medicine\", \"es\": \"Brindando Asistencia a Hospitales Venezolanos\"}', '{\"en\": \"Help Venezuelan Hospitals | Supplying Food and Medicine\", \"es\": \"<h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 42px; color: #282828; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: justify;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\">Resumen</strong></h2>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\\\">El sistema de salud en Venezuela est&aacute; disminuyendo cada vez m&aacute;s. Todos los d&iacute;as, se han publicado art&iacute;culos en la prensa denunciando el mal estado de los principales hospitales p&uacute;blicos en Venezuela. Cada vez m&aacute;s, la crisis de salud y la escasez de medicamentos se han presentado en el pa&iacute;s. El hospital Rafael Malpica, ubicado en Guacara solamente proporciona arroz para sus pacientes y en esta misma situaci&oacute;n se encuentra la mayor&iacute;a de los hospitales p&uacute;blicos en Venezuela. Las prote&iacute;nas no est&aacute;n incluidas en la dieta. Este proyecto se destinar&aacute; a la alimentaci&oacute;n de adultos y ni&ntilde;os vulnerables en diferentes hospitales alrededor de dicho pa&iacute;s.</span></p>\"}', '{\"en\": \"<iframe class=\\\"ifrimi\\\" src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/hospitals-us?only_donation_meter=true&amp;donation_meter_color=%232ecc71\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\" max-height: 93px !important; height: 92px;\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" data-donorbox-id=\\\"DonorBox-f1\\\"></iframe><iframe class=\\\"aframa\\\" src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/hospitals-us?hide_donation_meter=true\\\" height=\\\"685px\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\" max-height: none !important; height: 1139px;\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" allowpaymentrequest=\\\"\\\" data-donorbox-id=\\\"DonorBox-f2\\\"></iframe>\", \"es\": \"<script src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/widget.js\\\" paypalExpress=\\\"false\\\"></script><iframe src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/hospitales-us?default_interval=o&hide_donation_meter=true&enable_auto_scroll=false\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" allowpaymentrequest=\\\"allowpaymentrequest\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" height=\\\"900px\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\"max-width: 500px; min-width: 250px; max-height:none!important\\\"></iframe>\"}', '{\"en\": \"<iframe class=\\\"embed-responsive-item\\\" src=\\\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dDJ4JCiDdH4?feature=oembed\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allow=\\\"autoplay; encrypted-media\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"\\\"></iframe>\", \"es\": null}', '{\"en\": {\"special_tag\": \"Urgent Help\", \"description_heading\": \"Description Heading\", \"description_text\": \"Detailed Description\", \"summary_title\": \"Summary\", \"summary_text\": \"The health care system in Venezuela is declining rapidly. Each day, the press denounces the failing state of public hospitals. Increasingly, the health care crisis and the shortage of medicine and food have plagued the country. The Rafael Malpica hospital, located in Guacara (Valencia, Venezuela) is providing only rice for their patients. Many other hospitals are facing the same situation. Proteins are never included in their diet… This project will feed vulnerable adults and children in different hospitals.\", \"help_mini_title\": \"Help People In need\", \"help_title\": \"Start Donating Today, Make The Difference\", \"help_btn_text\": \"DONATE TO THIS PROJECT >\"}, \"es\": {\"special_tag\": \"Ayuda urgente\", \"description_heading\": \"Subtitulo por defecto\", \"description_text\": \"Texto de descripción por defecto\", \"summary_title\": \"Resumen\", \"summary_text\": \"The health care system in Venezuela is declining rapidly. Each day, the press denounces the failing state of public hospitals. Increasingly, the health care crisis and the shortage of medicine and food have plagued the country. The Rafael Malpica hospital, located in Guacara (Valencia, Venezuela) is providing only rice for their patients. Many other hospitals are facing the same situation. Proteins are never included in their diet… This project will feed vulnerable adults and children in different hospitals.\", \"help_mini_title\": \"Ayuda a personas en necesidad\", \"help_title\": \"Comienza a donar hoy, Haz la diferencia\", \"help_btn_text\": \"DONAR A ESTE PROYECTO >\"}}', '{\"en\": \"<h2>Challenge</h2><p>What is the challenge? According to FAO, in the Global Report on Food Crisis 2017, the worsening economic situation in Venezuela has caused a severe shortage of food and medicine. Many refer to this as <a href=\\\"https://edition.cnn.com/2017/04/21/americas/venezuela-crisis-explained/index.html\\\">The ‘Maduro diet’</a>. Medical supplies are not being imported to Venezuela. This serious crisis is causing malnutrition, which is far from being alleviated. Hospitals in Venezuela are not providing enough meals for all their patients. Some are only providing rice as their main meal. Most of the patients get thinner day-by-day. It seems that they get sicker during their stay at the hospital due to lack of protein. A well-balanced meal and proper medication are required for a successful recovery.</p><h2>Solution</h2><p>South American Initiative will continue providing meals and clean drinking water to children and adults who are suffering from malnutrition in hospitals. New and expecting mothers will receive all help they need to take care of their babies with things like diapers, formula, feeding bottles, and other supplies with your donations.</p><h2>Long-Term Impact</h2><p>There is a large number of patients distributed across different hospitals Venezuela who are not being well fed. By providing a balanced meal to each one of them these patients will achieve better recovery; they can return home enjoying good health.</p><h3>Donate To Help Venezuela Today</h3><p>Make a tax deductible donation to <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/project/help-venezuela/\\\">help Venezuela</a> from our website.<a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/\\\"> South American Initiative </a>are a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization committed to providing relief to poverty-stricken people.</p>\", \"es\": \"<h2>Desafío</h2><p>Según la FAO en su Informe global sobre las crisis alimentaria de 2017 observa que el empeoramiento de la situación económica en Venezuela puede causar una grave escasez de bienes de consumo incluidos alimentos y medicinas.</p><h2>Solución</h2><p>Al momento de ejecutar este proyecto el equipo de Iniciativa Suramericana continuará brindando alimentos y agua potable a niños y adultos que sufren desnutrición.</p><h2>Impacto a Largo Tiempo</h2><p>Hay una gran cantidad de pacientes distribuidos en diferentes hospitales en toda Venezuela que no están bien alimentados al proporcionar una alimentación balanceada estos pacientes lograrán mejor recuperación.</p>\"}', '{\"en\": \"Help hospitals in Venezuela with your tax deductible donation. Support those who need medicatino and food in under funded hospitals across Venezuela.\", \"es\": \"\"}', '{}', 'published', NULL, 1, '2025-07-21 17:32:11', '2025-07-21 17:32:11'),
(118, '{\"en\": \"help-venezuelan-orphans\", \"es\": \"huerfanos\"}', '{\"en\": \"Help Venezuelan Orphans\", \"es\": \"Ayuda a los Huérfanos de Venezuela | South American Initiative\"}', '{\"en\": \"Help Venezuelan Orphans | Providing 1,500 Meals Weekly\", \"es\": \"<h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 42px; color: #282828; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: justify;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\">Resumen</strong></h2>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\\\">La crisis alimentaria en Venezuela perjudica a todos los componentes de la sociedad. Nadie parece escapar de la realidad que comienza a dejar da&ntilde;os permanentes para las generaciones futuras. El 33% de los ni&ntilde;os tiene un retraso en el crecimiento y este es un da&ntilde;o mental que les acompa&ntilde;ar&aacute; durante toda su vida. La desnutrici&oacute;n est&aacute; cobrando vidas en los orfanatos debido a la falta de suministros de alimentos proporcionados por el gobierno actual.</span></p>\"}', '{\"en\": \"<iframe class=\\\"aframa\\\" src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/orphans-us?hide_donation_meter=true\\\" height=\\\"685px\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\" max-height: none !important; height: 1257px;\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" allowpaymentrequest=\\\"\\\" data-donorbox-id=\\\"DonorBox-f2\\\"></iframe>\", \"es\": \"<script src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/widget.js\\\" paypalExpress=\\\"false\\\"></script><iframe src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/huerfanos-us?default_interval=o&hide_donation_meter=true\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" allowpaymentrequest=\\\"allowpaymentrequest\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" height=\\\"900px\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\"max-width: 500px; min-width: 250px; max-height:none!important\\\"></iframe>\"}', '{\"en\": \"<iframe class=\\\"embed-responsive-item\\\" src=\\\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/r02cAwXXJ58?feature=oembed\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allow=\\\"autoplay; encrypted-media\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"\\\"></iframe>\", \"es\": null}', '{\"en\": {\"special_tag\": \"Urgent Help\", \"description_heading\": \"Description Heading\", \"description_text\": \"Detailed Description\", \"summary_title\": \"Summary\", \"summary_text\": \"The food crisis in Venezuela harms all components of society. No one seems to escape the reality which begins to leave permanent damages for future generations. 33% of children have a growth delay and this is a mental damage that will be with them throughout their lives. Malnutrition is taking lives in orphanages due to the lack of food supplies provided by the current government.\", \"help_mini_title\": \"Help People In need\", \"help_title\": \"Start Donating Today, Make The Difference\", \"help_btn_text\": \"DONATE TO THIS PROJECT >\"}, \"es\": {\"special_tag\": \"Ayuda urgente\", \"description_heading\": \"Subtitulo por defecto\", \"description_text\": \"Texto de descripción por defecto\", \"summary_title\": \"Resumen\", \"summary_text\": \"The food crisis in Venezuela harms all components of society. No one seems to escape the reality which begins to leave permanent damages for future generations. 33% of children have a growth delay and this is a mental damage that will be with them throughout their lives. Malnutrition is taking lives in orphanages due to the lack of food supplies provided by the current government.\", \"help_mini_title\": \"Ayuda a personas en necesidad\", \"help_title\": \"Comienza a donar hoy, Haz la diferencia\", \"help_btn_text\": \"DONAR A ESTE PROYECTO >\"}}', '{\"en\": \"<h2>Challenge</h2>\\n<p>The scarcity of food in Venezuela and the lack of medical supplies has become a problem that affects the health of vulnerable starving children. Orphaned children do not receive the help promised by the government. Those in charge of orphanages have been tasked with reducing the amount of food per day for each per orphaned child. There are more children who are abandoned on the streets that have created an insurmountable challenge.</p>\\n<h2>Solution</h2>\\n<p>South American Initiative will continue to provide over 200 meals per day and clean drinking water to orphans in Venezuela and adults who are suffering from malnutrition in hospitals. We are currently providing shoes, food and clothes to orphanages located in the state of Carabobo, Venezuela \\\"Maria Auxiliadora\\\", \\\"Semillita del Inmaculado Corazon de Maria\\\" and \\\"San Antonio\\\" and expanding to more. We are helping to cover the basic needs of each orphaned child who temporarily lives in these places. Also, we are currently investing in agriculture and in building a greenhouse to plant vegetables and fruits to provide sustainable food for Venezuela orphanages across the country. A percentage of contributions goes towards these greenhouses.</p>\\n<h2>How can I help Venezuela orphans?</h2>\\n<p>This project will help more than 500 orphans through a diet that provides all the necessary nutrients for the healthy development of each child. By providing a balanced fresh meal to each one of them, these children can be well educated and become productive members in society. Help orphans in need, help sponsor an orphan charity, help sponsor a child.</p>\\n<h3>Donate To Help Venezuela Today</h3>\\n<p>Make a tax deductible donation to <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/project/help-venezuela/\\\" title=\\\"Help Venezuela\\\">help Venezuela</a> from our website. <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/\\\" title=\\\"South American Initiative\\\">South American Initiative</a> are a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization committed to providing relief to the most poverty-stricken people and areas of our beloved Venezuelan nation. Your secure online donation will help provide necessary food, clothes, and more to Venezuelan orphans, <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/project/hospitals/\\\" title=\\\"Hospitals\\\">hospitals</a>, and more. Learn more about our organization when you visit our <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/about-us/\\\" title=\\\"About Us\\\">about us</a> page.</p>\\n<h2>Related Articles</h2>\\n<ul><li><a href=\\\"https://www.efe.com/efe/english/world/abandoned-minors-roam-the-streets-of-venezuela-after-parents-leave-country/50000262-3542501\\\">Abandoned minors roam the streets of Venezuela after parents leave country.</a> - Agency EFE.</li><li><a href=\\\"https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/hundreds-of-children-in-venezuela-are-starving-to-death-nytimes-reports_us_5a380d7fe4b0fc99878dd05d\\\">Hundreds Of Children In Venezuela Are Starving To Death, Says New York Times Report.</a> - Huffington Post </li><li><a href=\\\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/290225097_Street_Children_and_Adolescents_in_Venezuela_A_public_problem\\\">Street Children and Adolescents in Venezuela: A public problem?</a> - ResearchGate</li></ul>\", \"es\": \"<h2>Desafío</h2>\\n<p>La escasez de alimentos en Venezuela y la falta de suministros médicos se ha convertido en un problema que afecta la salud de los niños vulnerables que pasan hambre. Los niños huérfanos no reciben la ayuda prometida por el gobierno. A los encargados de los orfanatos se les ha encomendado la tarea de reducir la cantidad de alimentos por día por cada niño huérfano. Hay más niños que son abandonados y en las calles que han creado un desafío insuperable.</p>\\n<h2>Solución</h2>\\n<p>Iniciativa Suramericana continuará brindando más de 240 comidas por día y agua potable para huérfanos en Venezuela y para aquellos que sufren de desnutrición en los hospitales. También proporcionamos zapatos y ropa a orfanatos ubicados en el estado de Carabobo, Venezuela: \\\"María Auxiliadora\\\", \\\"Semillita del Inmaculado Corazón de María\\\" y \\\"San Antonio\\\", y continuamos en expansión. Estamos ayudando a cubrir las necesidades básicas de cada niño huérfano que vive temporalmente en estos lugares.Además, actualmente estamos invirtiendo en agricultura y en la construcción de un invernadero para plantar vegetales y frutas para proporcionar alimentos sostenibles a los orfanatos de todo el país.Un porcentaje de las contribuciones va hacia estos invernaderos.</p>\\n<h2>Impacto a largo Tiempo</h2>\\n<p>Este proyecto ayudará a más de 500 huérfanos mediante una dieta que proporcione todos los nutrientes necesarios para el desarrollo saludable de cada niño.Al ofrecer una comida equilibrada y fresca a cada uno de ellos, estos niños pueden ser bien educados y convertirse en miembros productivos de la sociedad.Ayuda a los huérfanos que lo necesiten; ayúdanos patrocinando una obra benéfica o apadrinando un niño.&iexcl;Ayúdanos salvaráVenezuela!</p>\\n<h2>&Artículos Relacionados;</h2><ul><li><span style=\'color:#282828;font-family:\\\"Work Sans\\\";font-size:18px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0 .6px;text-align:justify;\'>1.&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\'color:#282828;font-family:\\\"Work Sans\\\";font-size:18px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0 .6px;text-align:justify;\'>Niños desamparadosdeambulanenVenezuelatraséxododesuspadres.-ElNacional<br /></span></li></ul>\"}', '{\"en\": \"Help Venezuela during this economic crisis. Support hospitals and orphanages that are suffering. Your donation is 501(c)(3) tax deductible.\", \"es\": \"\"}', '{}', 'published', NULL, 1, '2025-07-21 17:32:11', '2025-07-21 17:32:11'),
(119, '{\"en\": \"help-abandoned-venezuelan-pets\", \"es\": \"ayudando-a-mascotas-abandonadas-en-venezuela\"}', '{\"en\": \"Help Abandoned Venezuelan Pets\", \"es\": \"Ayudando a Mascotas Abandonadas en Venezuela\"}', '{\"en\": \"Help Abandoned Venezuelan Pets | Providing Food and Care\", \"es\": \"<h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 42px; color: #282828; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: justify;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\">Resumen</strong></h2>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\\\">Hay miles de perros vagando en las calles de Venezuela. Perros hambrientos, enfermos, lastimados, abusados y abandonados. Los due&ntilde;os de perros de Venezuela han sido forzados a abandonar a sus mascotas porque la comida y medicinas se han vuelto inaccesibles monetariamente debido a la crisis econ&oacute;mica que invade la naci&oacute;n. Por ello hemos venido al rescate. SAI-A&amp;G ha construido el santuario m&aacute;s grande de perros en Venezuela para rescatar, brindar soporte m&eacute;dico y refugio a los perros sin hogar.</span></p>\"}', '{\"en\": \"<iframe class=\\\"ifrimi\\\" src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/pets-us?only_donation_meter=true&amp;donation_meter_color=%232ecc71\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\" max-height: 93px !important; height: 92px;\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" data-donorbox-id=\\\"DonorBox-f1\\\"></iframe> <iframe class=\\\"aframa\\\" src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/pets-us?hide_donation_meter=true\\\" height=\\\"685px\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\"max-height: none !important; height: 1239px;\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" allowpaymentrequest=\\\"\\\" data-donorbox-id=\\\"DonorBox-f2\\\"></iframe>\", \"es\": \"<script src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/widget.js\\\" paypalExpress=\\\"false\\\"></script><iframe src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/mascotas-us?default_interval=o&hide_donation_meter=true\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" allowpaymentrequest=\\\"allowpaymentrequest\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" height=\\\"900px\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\"max-width: 500px; min-width: 250px; max-height:none!important\\\"></iframe>\"}', '{\"en\": null, \"es\": null}', '{\"en\": {\"special_tag\": \"Urgent Help\", \"description_heading\": \"Description Heading\", \"description_text\": \"Detailed Description\", \"summary_title\": \"Summary\", \"summary_text\": \"There are tens of thousands of dogs roaming the streets of Venezuela! The dogs are starving, injured, sick, abused and neglected. Dog owners in Venezuela have been forced to abandon their pets because dog food and medical care has become unaffordable due to the economic crisis plaguing the country. We have come to the rescue! SAI-A&G has built the largest no-kill sanctuary in Venezuela to rescue, rehabilitate, provide medical care, neutering/spaying and shelter to homeless dogs!\", \"help_mini_title\": \"Help People In need\", \"help_title\": \"Start Donating Today, Make The Difference\", \"help_btn_text\": \"DONATE TO THIS PROJECT >\"}, \"es\": {\"special_tag\": \"Ayuda urgente\", \"description_heading\": \"Subtitulo por defecto\", \"description_text\": \"Texto de descripción por defecto\", \"summary_title\": \"Resumen\", \"summary_text\": \"\", \"help_mini_title\": \"Ayuda a personas en necesidad\", \"help_title\": \"Comienza a donar hoy, Haz la diferencia\", \"help_btn_text\": \"DONAR A ESTE PROYECTO >\"}}', '{\"en\": \"<h2>Challenge</h2><p>There are starving, diseased, injured, neglected dogs roaming the streets of Venezuela. Since many people in the country are unable to afford medical care and food for their dogs, people abandon their dogs and the dogs are forced to live on the streets. The atrocity is caused by the severe collapse of Venezuela\'s economy, government services, and government infrastructure.</p><h2>Solution</h2><p>SAI-A&G Sanctuary rescues and rehabilitates abandoned dogs at our facility. Dogs are cared for by our veterinarian and his team and brought back to health, neutered/spayed, and given life-saving medication and vaccinations. Our facility has a surgery room, over 2 acres of outdoor space, dog cots, automated water fountains, and containment areas for sick rescues and aggressive dogs. We are a no-kill sanctuary. We also provide food and medical services to partner shelters.</p><h3>Long-Term Impact</h3><p>SAI-A&G Sanctuary will continue to rescue dogs and provide medical care, food, spaying/neutering,and long-term care with hopeful adoptions. SAI-A&G will expand the number of partner shelters that receive food, medical care and medicine and increase the number of states where we are able to assist.</p><h3>Donate To Help Venezuela Today</h3><p>Make a tax deductible donation to <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/project/help-venezuela/\\\" title=\\\"help Venezuela\\\">help Venezuela</a> from our website. <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/\\\" title=\\\"South American Initiative\\\">South American Initiative</a> is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization committed to providing relief to the most poverty-stricken people and areas of our beloved Venezuelan nation. Your secure online donation will help provide necessary food, clothes,and more to <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/project/orphans-venezuela/\\\" title=\\\"Venezuelan orphans\\\">Venezuelan orphans</a>, <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/project/hospitals/\\\" title=\\\"hospitals\\\">hospitals</a>,and more.Learn more about our organization when you visit our <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/about-us/\\\" title=\\\"about us\\\">about us</a> page.</p>\", \"es\": \"<h2>Desafío</h2><p>Hay muchos perros hambrientos,enfermos,lastimados y rechazados vagando en las calles de Venezuela.Debido a que muchas personas en el país se han encontrado incapaces de costear sus gastos médicos y alimenticios,se ven obligadas a abandonar a sus mascotas y forzarlas a vivir en la calle.Esta catástrofe se origina por el severo colapso de la infraestructura política,económica y la decadencia de los servicios públicos en Venezuela.</p><h2>Solución</h2><p>En el santuario de perros de SAI-A&G nos encargamos de rescatar y rehabilitar perros abandonados en nuestras instalaciones.Los perros son tratados por nuestro equipo de voluntarios y veterinario quienes les brindan el cuidado médico necesario y las vacunas que los perros necesiten para recuperar su salud.Nuestras instalaciones cuentan con más de 2 acres de terreno un cuarto de cirugía,camas para perros fuentes automáticas,y un área de cuarentena para perros enfermos o agresivos.Somos un santuario que no sacrifica perros además proveemos comida y medicinas a varios refugios asociados con nosotros.</p>\"}', '{\"en\": \"Animals in Venezuela are suffering. SAI will help through alliances with other non-profit organizations to supply provisions for necessary care.\", \"es\": \"\"}', '{}', 'published', NULL, 1, '2025-07-21 17:32:11', '2025-07-21 17:32:11'),
(120, '{\"en\": \"help-venezuelan-refugees\", \"es\": \"fondo-para-venezolanos-refugiados\"}', '{\"en\": \"Help Venezuelan Refugees\", \"es\": \"Fondo Para Venezolanos Refugiados\"}', '{\"en\": \"Help Venezuela\'s Refugee Crisis %%page%% - 501(c)(3) Nonprofit Organization\", \"es\": \"<h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 42px; color: #282828; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\">Resumen</strong></span></h2>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\\\">Familias enteras se ven obligadas a abandonar sus hogares con solo lo que pueden cargar a sus espaldas. El largo viaje a trav&eacute;s de la frontera con Colombia se ha vuelto muy com&uacute;n en estos d&iacute;as. La mayor&iacute;a de los refugiados venezolanos que llegan a Colombia duermen en campos de refugiados, est&aacute;n desempleados y no tienen suficiente comida. Este fondo apoyar&aacute; a los refugiados venezolanos. Trabajaremos con otras organizaciones en la frontera entre Colombia y Venezuela que se comprometan a brindar asistencia y apoyo a quienes lo necesiten.</span></p>\"}', '{\"en\": \"<iframe class=\\\"ifrimi\\\" src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/venezuelan-refugee-fund?only_donation_meter=true&amp;donation_meter_color=%232ecc71\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\" max-height: 93px !important; height: 92px;\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" data-donorbox-id=\\\"DonorBox-f1\\\"></iframe><iframe class=\\\"aframa\\\" src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/venezuelan-refugee-fund?hide_donation_meter=true\\\" height=\\\"685px\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\" max-height: none !important; height: 1167px;\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" allowpaymentrequest=\\\"\\\" data-donorbox-id=\\\"DonorBox-f2\\\"></iframe>\", \"es\": \"<script src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/widget.js\\\" paypalExpress=\\\"false\\\"></script><iframe src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/fondo-venezolanos-refugiados\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" allowpaymentrequest=\\\"allowpaymentrequest\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" height=\\\"900px\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\"max-width: 500px; min-width: 250px; max-height:none!important\\\"></iframe>\"}', '{\"en\": null, \"es\": null}', '{\"en\": {\"special_tag\": \"Urgent Help\", \"description_heading\": \"Description Heading\", \"description_text\": \"Detailed Description\", \"summary_title\": \"Summary\", \"summary_text\": \"Entire families are forced to leave their homes with only what they can carry on their backs. The long journey across the Colombian border has become very common these days. The majority of Venezuelan refugees, who make it into Colombia, are sleeping in refugee camps, unemployed and without enough food. This fund will support Venezuelan refugees. We will work with other organizations in the Colombia–Venezuela border who are committed to providing assistance and support to those in need.\", \"help_mini_title\": \"Help People In need\", \"help_title\": \"Start Donating Today, Make The Difference\", \"help_btn_text\": \"DONATE TO THIS PROJECT >\"}, \"es\": {\"special_tag\": \"Ayuda urgente\", \"description_heading\": \"Subtitulo por defecto\", \"description_text\": \"Texto de descripción por defecto\", \"summary_title\": \"Resumen\", \"summary_text\": \"Entire families are forced to leave their homes with only what they can carry on their backs. The long journey across the Colombian border has become very common these days. The majority of Venezuelan refugees, who make it into Colombia, are sleeping in refugee camps, unemployed and without enough food. This fund will support Venezuelan refugees. We will work with other organizations in the Colombia–Venezuela border who are committed to providing assistance and support to those in need.\", \"help_mini_title\": \"Ayuda a personas en necesidad\", \"help_title\": \"Comienza a donar hoy, Haz la diferencia\", \"help_btn_text\": \"DONAR A ESTE PROYECTO >\"}}', '{\"en\": \"<h2>Challenge</h2><p>Due to hyper-inflation caused by the failing government, many Venezuelans are fleeing the country. According to the Colombian government, one million Venezuelans have entered Columbia and 660,000 have remained. The WFP estimates that 90% of these refugees do not have enough food and medical supplies to survive.</p><h2>Solution</h2><p>This fund is helping to provide life-saving relief efforts to Venezuelan refugees living in refugee camps. In addition, the fund is assisting the communities that are receiving the refugees and helping them through their migration. SAI is committed to providing food, medicine and job training to refugees in need.</p><h2>Long-term impact</h2><p>South American Initiative and its partners are working diligently to help Venezuelan refugees. SAI is devoted to continuing its effort in Venezuela until the food and medical shortage is resolved.</p><h3>Donate To Help Venezuela Today</h3><p>Make a tax deductible donation to <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/project/help-venezuela/\\\" title=\\\"Help Venezuela\\\">help Venezuela</a> from our website. <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/\\\" title=\\\"South American Initiative\\\">South American Initiative</a> are a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization committed to providing relief to the most poverty stricken people and areas of our beloved Venezuelan nation. Your secure online donation will help provide necessary food, clothes, and more for <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/project/orphans-venezuela/\\\" title=\\\"Venezuelan orphans\\\">Venezuelan orphans</a>, <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/project/hospitals/\\\" title=\\\"Hospitals\\\">hospitals</a>, and more. Learn more about our organization when you visit our <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/about-us/\\\" title=\\\"About Us\\\">about us</a> page.</p>\", \"es\": \"<h2>Desafío</h2><p>Debido a la hiperinflación causada por el gobierno en quiebra, muchos venezolanos están huyendo del país. Según el gobierno colombiano, un millón de venezolanos ingresaron a Colombia y se han quedado 660,000. El PMA estima que el 90% de estos refugiados no tienen suficientes alimentos y suministros médicos para sobrevivir.</p><h2>Solución</h2><p>Este fondo brindará ayuda humanitaria y de socorro a los refugiados venezolanos que viven en campos de refugiados. Además, el fondo ayudará a las comunidades que reciben a los refugiados y ayudar a los venezolanos a través de su migración. SAI se compromete a proporcionar alimentos, medicinas y capacitación laboral a los refugiados necesitados.</p><h2>Impacto a largo Tiempo</h2><p>Iniciativa Suramericana y sus patrocinadores están trabajando diligentemente para ayudar a los refugiados venezolanos. SAI está dedicada a continuar su esfuerzo para ayudar a las familias a transitar hacia sus nuevas vidas.</p>\"}', '{\"en\": \"Do your part to help during the Venezuela refugee crisis. Donate now with a tax deductible gift to help those most in need during this crisis.\", \"es\": \"\"}', '{}', 'published', NULL, 1, '2025-07-21 17:32:11', '2025-07-21 17:32:11'),
(121, '{\"en\": \"endangered-animal-rescue-fund-zoo-animal-venezuelan-sai\", \"es\": \"fondo-para-rescatar-animales-en-peligro-de-extinción\"}', '{\"en\": \"Endangered Animal Rescue Fund - Zoo Animal Venezuelan - SAI\", \"es\": \"Fondo para rescatar animales en peligro de extinción \"}', '{\"en\": \"Endangered Animal Rescue Fund - Help Zoo Animal Venezuela - SAI\", \"es\": \"<h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 42px; color: #282828; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: justify;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\">Resumen</strong></h2>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\\\">Debido a la actual situaci&oacute;n econ&oacute;mica y pol&iacute;tica que azota a Venezuela, grandes cantidades de animales del zool&oacute;gico est&aacute;n muriendo o est&aacute;n desnutridos. Muchos de estos zool&oacute;gicos han visto a sus animales en peligro de muerte debido al hambre y la falta de atenci&oacute;n m&eacute;dica. No hay suficiente dinero o recursos para alimentar y atender a los animales en estos zool&oacute;gicos.</span></p>\"}', '{\"en\": \"<iframe class=\\\"ifrimi\\\" src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/endangered-animal-rescue-fund?a=b\\\" height=\\\"685px\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\"max-height: none !important; height: 1085px;\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" data-donorbox-id=\\\"DonorBox-f1\\\" allowpaymentrequest=\\\"true\\\"></iframe>\", \"es\": \"<iframe class=\\\"ifrimi\\\" src=\\\"https://donorbox.org/embed/endangered-animal-rescue-fund?a=b\\\" height=\\\"685px\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\"max-height: none !important; height: 1085px;\\\" seamless=\\\"seamless\\\" name=\\\"donorbox\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" scrolling=\\\"no\\\" data-donorbox-id=\\\"DonorBox-f1\\\" allowpaymentrequest=\\\"true\\\"></iframe>\"}', '{\"en\": null, \"es\": null}', '{\"en\": {\"special_tag\": \"Urgent Help\", \"description_heading\": \"Description Heading\", \"description_text\": \"Detailed Description\", \"summary_title\": \"Summary\", \"summary_text\": \"Due to the current political and economic situation plaguing Venezuela, large amounts of zoo animals are dying or are malnourished. Many of these zoos have had their animals become endangered due to starvation and lack of medical care. There is not enough money or resources to feed and care for animals in these zoos.\", \"help_mini_title\": \"Help People In need\", \"help_title\": \"Start Donating Today, Make The Difference\", \"help_btn_text\": \"DONATE TO THIS PROJECT >\"}, \"es\": {\"special_tag\": \"Ayuda urgente\", \"description_heading\": \"Subtitulo por defecto\", \"description_text\": \"Texto de descripción por defecto\", \"summary_title\": \"Resumen\", \"summary_text\": \"Debido a la actual situación económica y política que azota a Venezuela, grandes cantidades de animales del zoológico están muriendo o están desnutridos. Muchos de estos zoológicos han visto a sus animales en peligro de muerte debido al hambre y la falta de atención médica. No hay suficiente dinero o recursos para alimentar y atender a los animales en estos zoológicos.\", \"help_mini_title\": \"Ayuda a personas en necesidad\", \"help_title\": \"Comienza a donar hoy, Haz la diferencia\", \"help_btn_text\": \"DONAR A ESTE PROYECTO >\"}}', '{\"en\": \"<h2>Challenge</h2><p>Due to current government corruption, there have been difficulties with the animals getting the help they need. The private zoos suffer because of the economic crash and lessening of tourism as a result of the crisis. The public zoos suffer the worst because of the lack of funds and corruption from the current regime. The challenge is being able to identify the needs of private and public zoos and getting food and medical treatment.</p><h2>Solution</h2><p>South American Initiative will step in to fill this gap providing food and medical care to neglected animals that are suffering in these zoos. We are presently working with two zoos and one animal refuge in providing food and medical care to these animals, and plan to work with many more.</p><h2>Long-Term Impact</h2><p>South American Initiative’s long-term goal is to feed sick and neglected animals, providing them with the proper care and nutrition in zoos throughout Venezuela. With your support, we will save these animals and be able to expand our resources throughout the country.</p><h3>Donate To Help Venezuela Today</h3><p>Make a tax deductible donation to <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/project/help-venezuela/\\\" title=\\\"help Venezuela\\\">help Venezuela</a> from our website. <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/\\\" title=\\\"South American Initiative\\\">South American Initiative</a> are a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization committed to providing relief to the most poverty stricken people and areas of our beloved Venezuelan nation. Your secure online donation will help provide necessary food, clothes, and more to <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/project/orphans-venezuela/\\\" title=\\\"Venezuelan orphans\\\">Venezuelan orphans</a>, <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/project/hospitals/\\\" title=\\\"hospitals\\\">hospitals</a>, and more. Learn more about our organization when you visit our <a href=\\\"https://sai.ngo/about-us/\\\" title=\\\"about us\\\">about us</a> page.</p>\", \"es\": \"<h2>Desafío</h2><p>Debido a la corrupción del gobierno actual, se han presentado muchos obstáculos para que los animales puedan recibir la ayuda que necesitan. Los zoológicos privados sufren debido al colapso económico y disminución del turismo como resultado de la crisis. Los zoológicos públicos sufren más debido a la falta de fondos y la corrupción del régimen actual. El desafío es poder identificar las necesidades de los zoológicos públicos y privados y obtener alimentos y tratamientos médicos.</p><h2>Solución</h2><p>Iniciativa Suramericana intervendrá para llenar este vacío proporcionando alimentos y atención médica a los animales que están sufriendo en los zoológicos. Actualmente estamos ayudando a dos zoológicos y un refugio de animales proporcionándoles alimentos y atención médica a los animales, y planeamos ayudar a muchos otros más.</p><h2>Impacto a largo Tiempo</h2><p>El objetivo a largo plazo de Iniciativa Suramericana es alimentar a los animales enfermos y abandonados, brindándoles el cuidado y la nutrición adecuada en los zoológicos de Venezuela. Con tu apoyo, podremos salvar a estos animales y ser capaces de expandir nuestros recursos en todo el país.</p><h3>Dona Para Ayudar A Venezuela Hoy</h3><p>Realiza una donación deducible de impuestos para ayudar a Venezuela través nuestra página web. South American Initiative es una organización 501 (c) (3) sin fines de lucro comprometida a brindar alivio a las personas más afectadas por la pobreza de nuestra amada nación Venezolana. Tu donación en línea es segura y nos ayudará proveer comida, ropa y más huérfanos venezolanos, hospitales, entre otros.</p>\"}', '{\"en\": \"Help support endangered animals in zoos across Venezuela during this economic crisis. Your donation is tax deductible. Help Venezuela\'s animals today.\", \"es\": \"\"}', '{}', 'published', NULL, 1, '2025-07-21 17:32:11', '2025-07-21 17:32:11');
