at Ut wisi enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exerci tation ullamcorper suscipit lobortis nis ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis autem vel eum iriure dolor in hendrerit in vulputate velit esse molestie consequat, vel illum dolore eu feugiat nulla facilisis at vero eros et accumsan et iusto odio dignissim. Qui blandit praesent luptatum zzril delenit augue duis dolore te feugait nulla\", \"donate_title\": \"Help people in need\", \"donate_text\": \"START DONATING TODAY, MAKE THE DIFFERENCE\", \"donate_button\": \"\"}, \"es\": {\"h1_title\": \"SAI entrega comida y provee cuidado médico a orfanatos de Venezuela.\", \"posted_by\": \"\", \"h3_1\": \"\", \"paragraph_1\": \"\", \"paragraph_2\": \"\", \"h3_2\": \"\", \"paragraph_3\": \"\", \"donate_title\": \"\", \"donate_text\": \"\", \"donate_button\": \"\"}}', '{\"en\": \"<h1>SAI Provides Food and Medical Care to Orphans in Venezuela!</h1><br>\\r\\n<p>South America Initiative continues providing food and medical care to orphanages in Venezuela. From July to October 2022, the SAI food distribution program has provided over 15,400 meals to 337 orphans in five different orphanages that receive our support!</p>\\r\\n<p>SAI continues to provide ophans the following nutiritous food: rice, black beans, celery, green onion, fresh cilantro, chicken, sardines, potatoes, spaghetti, cornflour, tomatoes, carrots, wheat flour, and various fruit including papaya, bananas, strawberries, watermelons, pineapples, etc.</p>\\r\\n<p>Many of the orphans are afflicted by illnesses due to prior inadequate medical care and nutrition, the priority of SAI is to provide comprehensive healthcare to every orphan! Our goal is to ensure that these orphans are healthy and happy!</p>\\r\\n\", \"es\": \"<h1>SAI entrega comida y provee cuidado médico a orfanatos de Venezuela.</h1>\\r\\n<p>SAI entrega comida y provee cuidado médico a orfanatos de Venezuela.</p>\\r\\n<p>South America Initiative continua brindando ayuda médica y comida a orfanatos en Venezuela. Desde Julio hasta Octubre de 2022, SAI ha distribuido más de 15,400 platos de comida a 337 huerfanos en 5 orfanatos afiliados a nuestro programa.</p>\\r\\n<p>Entre los nutritivos alimentos que proveemos se encuentra: arroz, caraotas, apio, cebolla, cilantro, pollo, sardinas, papas, pasta, tómates, harina de maiz, zanahorias, harina de trigo, y frutas como; lechoza, bananas, fresas, sandias, piñas, etc.</p>\\r\\n<p>Muchos huerfanos son afectados por las inadeacuadas condiciones de los hospitales públicos y la mala alimentación, nuestra prioridad en SAI es brindar cuidado médico para todos los huerfanos. Nuestra meta es asegurar que cada uno de estos niños estén sanos y felices.</p>\\r\\n\"}', '{\"en\": {\"seo_title\": \"SAI Provides Food and Medical Care to Orphans in Venezuela!\", \"seo_description\": \"SAI Provides Food and Medical Care to Orphans in Venezuela!\", \"keywords\": null, \"og_title\": \"SAI Provides Food and Medical Care to Orphans in Venezuela!\", \"og_description\": \"SAI Provides Food and Medical Care to Orphans in Venezuela!\"}, \"es\": {\"seo_title\": \"SAI entrega comida y provee cuidado médico a orfanatos de Venezuela.\", \"seo_description\": \"SAI entrega comida y provee cuidado médico a orfanatos de Venezuela.\", \"keywords\": null, \"og_title\": \"SAI entrega comida y provee cuidado médico a orfanatos de Venezuela.\", \"og_description\": \"SAI entrega comida y provee cuidado médico a orfanatos de Venezuela.\"}}', 'published', 2, '2025-08-13 03:28:38', 1, 1, NULL, '2025-08-13 07:32:25'),
