ulla facilisis at vero eros et accumsan et iusto odio dignissim. Qui blandit praesent luptatum zzril delenit augue duis dolore te feugait nulla\", \"h3_2\": \"Lorem ipsum do\", \"paragraph_3\": \"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet dolore magna aliquam erat volutpat Ut wisi enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exerci tation ullamcorper suscipit lobortis nis ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis autem vel eum iriure dolor in hendrerit in vulputate velit esse molestie consequat, vel illum dolore eu feugiat nulla facilisis at vero eros et accumsan et iusto odio dignissim. Qui blandit praesent luptatum zzril delenit augue duis dolore te feugait nulla\", \"donate_title\": \"Help people in need\", \"donate_text\": \"START DONATING TODAY, MAKE THE DIFFERENCE\", \"donate_button\": \"\"}, \"es\": {\"h1_title\": \"Alimentando a niños huérfanos en Venezuela.\", \"posted_by\": \"\", \"h3_1\": \"\", \"paragraph_1\": \"\", \"paragraph_2\": \"\", \"h3_2\": \"\", \"paragraph_3\": \"\", \"donate_title\": \"\", \"donate_text\": \"\", \"donate_button\": \"\"}}', '{\"en\": \"<h1>Feeding Orphaned and Vulnerable Children</h1><br>\\r\\n<p>Every moment we dedicate ourselves to the orphans in Venezuela, we at South American Initiative feel driven to continue spreading our cause to help more children throughout Venezuela. Every donation represents another opportunity for us to not only give food, but also smiles and hope.</p>\\r\\n<p>The orphanages receive support from us and it is all thanks to our faithful donors that we have been able to continuously provide more food and supplies to the orphans. We appreciate the support from all of our donors who make it possible for us to continue providing life-sustaining food and supplies to these orphanages during Venezuela’s economic crisis.</p>\\r\\n<p>Over the past three months, SAI and GlobalGiving have provided the following number of meals to orphans in Venezuela:</p>\\r\\n<p>JULY: 4,830 meals</p>\\r\\n<p>were provided to orphans.</p>\\r\\n<p>AUGUST: 6,118 meals</p>\\r\\n<p>were provided to orphans.</p>\\r\\n<p>SEPTEMBER: 5,152 meals</p>\\r\\n<p>were provided to orphans</p>\\r\\n<p>Total of meals distributed over the past three months: 16,100</p>\\r\\n<p>Your contributions to South American Initiative make the expansion of this project a reality and increase the number of nutritious meals and supplies available to struggling orphanages.</p>\\r\\n<p>We at SAI want to thank each of our donors for their generosity in helping us improve the lives of orphans in Venezuela.</p>\\r\\n\", \"es\": \"<h1>Alimentando a niños huérfanos en Venezuela.</h1>\\r\\n<p>Cada momento que dedicamos a los niños huérfanos en Venezuela desde South American Initiative, nos sentimos impulsados ​​a seguir difundiendo nuestra causa para ayudar a más niños en toda Venezuela. Cada donación representa otra oportunidad para nosotros no solo por la comida que entregamos, sino también por ver sus sonrisas y esperanza.</p>\\r\\n<p>Los orfanatos reciben nuestro apoyo gracias a nuestros fieles donantes que nos permiten proporcionar continuamente más alimentos y suministros a los niños huérfanos. Agradecemos el apoyo de todos nuestros donantes que hacen posible que podamos continuar brindando alimentos y suministros vitales a estos orfanatos durante la crisis económica de Venezuela.</p>\\r\\n<p>Durante los últimos tres meses, SAI y GlobalGiving han proporcionado la siguiente cantidad de comidas a niños huérfanos en Venezuela:</p>\\r\\n<p>Se entregaron 4.830 comidas a los orfanatos.</p>\\r\\n<p>Se entregaron 6.118 comidas a los orfanatos.</p>\\r\\n<p>: Se entregaron 5.152 comidas a los orfanatos.</p>\\r\\n<p>Total de comidas distribuidas en los últimos tres meses:</p>\\r\\n<p>Sus contribuciones a South American initiative hacen realidad la expansión de este proyecto y aumentan la cantidad de comidas y suministros nutritivos disponibles para los orfanatos en dificultades.</p>\\r\\n<p>En SAI queremos agradecer a cada uno de nuestros donantes por su generosidad por ayudarnos a mejorar las vidas de los niños huérfanos en Venezuela.</p>\\r\\n\"}', '{\"en\": {\"seo_title\": \"Feeding Orphaned and Vulnerable Children\", \"seo_description\": \"Every moment we dedicate ourselves to the orphans in Venezuela, we at South American Initiative feel driven to continue spreading our cause to help more children throughout Venezuela. Every donation represents another opportunity for us to not only give food, but also smiles and hope.\", \"keywords\": \"Alimentando a niños huérfanos en Venezuela.\", \"og_title\": \"Feeding Orphaned and Vulnerable Children\", \"og_description\": \"Every moment we dedicate ourselves to the orphans in Venezuela, we at South American Initiative feel driven to continue spreading our cause to help more children throughout Venezuela. Every donation represents another opportunity for us to not only give food, but also smiles and hope.\"}, \"es\": {\"seo_title\": \"Alimentando a niños huérfanos en Venezuela.\", \"seo_description\": \"Alimentando a niños huérfanos en Venezuela.\", \"keywords\": null, \"og_title\": \"Alimentando a niños huérfanos en Venezuela.\", \"og_description\": \"Alimentando a niños huérfanos en Venezuela.\"}}', 'published', 3, '2025-08-13 17:08:54', 1, 1, NULL, '2025-08-13 21:12:27'),
