quip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis autem vel eum iriure dolor in hendrerit in vulputate velit esse molestie consequat, vel illum dolore eu feugiat nulla facilisis at vero eros et accumsan et iusto odio dignissim. Qui blandit praesent luptatum zzril delenit augue duis dolore te feugait nulla\", \"h3_2\": \"Lorem ipsum do\", \"paragraph_3\": \"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet dolore magna aliquam erat volutpat Ut wisi enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exerci tation ullamcorper suscipit lobortis nis ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis autem vel eum iriure dolor in hendrerit in vulputate velit esse molestie consequat, vel illum dolore eu feugiat nulla facilisis at vero eros et accumsan et iusto odio dignissim. Qui blandit praesent luptatum zzril delenit augue duis dolore te feugait nulla\", \"donate_title\": \"Help people in need\", \"donate_text\": \"START DONATING TODAY, MAKE THE DIFFERENCE\", \"donate_button\": \"\"}, \"es\": {\"h1_title\": \"Clínica SAI: Transformando Vidas en Venezuela – ¡716 Pacientes Atendidos con Cuidado Ampliado y Medicinas Gratis en 2023!\", \"posted_by\": \"\", \"h3_1\": \"\", \"paragraph_1\": \"\", \"paragraph_2\": \"\", \"h3_2\": \"\", \"paragraph_3\": \"\", \"donate_title\": \"\", \"donate_text\": \"\", \"donate_button\": \"\"}}', '{\"en\": \"<h1>SAI Medical Clinic: Transforming Lives in Venezuela – 716 Patients Helped with Expanded Care and Free Medicines in 2023!</h1><br>\\r\\n<p>We have great news! We are delighted to announce that the SAI Medical Clinic has expanded its waiting room which has increased the capacity of patients that we can receive every day, letting us help more people. Our clinic is now larger and we are thrilled to help more people with their health needs. A television has been added to the newly renovated waiting room to provide entertainment to children. We thank you for your support in saving lives.</p>\\r\\n<p>We are glad to report that 716 patients, including children, pregnant women, elders, newborns, and orphans, received medical attention at SAI Medical Clinic during the course of the last three months. Our free services have included physical exams, EKG evaluations, diagnostic gynecological and obstetric ultrasound services, infant wellness checks, dietary advice, and monthly check-ups for expectant moms. Additionally, we have been able to provide our patients with free medications, vitamins, and nutritional supplements.</p>\\r\\n<p>At SAI, our passion and mission are to improve lives. We cordially welcome you to join us in creating genuine change by giving on a regular basis. We can work together to save lives and give those in need better futures with your support!</p>\\r\\n<p>Become a monthly donor and let´s work toward a brighter future for in Venezuela. Thank you.</p>\\r\\n\", \"es\": \"<h1>Clínica SAI: Transformando Vidas en Venezuela – ¡716 Pacientes Atendidos con Cuidado Ampliado y Medicinas Gratis en 2023!</h1>\\r\\n<p>Por Jean Pérez - Líder del Proyecto</p>\\r\\n<p>¡Tenemos grandes noticias! Estamos encantados de anunciar que la Clínica Médica SAI ha ampliado su sala de espera, lo que ha aumentado la capacidad de pacientes que podemos recibir cada día, permitiéndonos ayudar a más personas. Nuestra clínica es ahora más grande y estamos encantados de poder ayudar a más personas con sus necesidades de salud. Se ha añadido un televisor a la sala de espera recién renovada para entretener a los niños. Les agradecemos su apoyo para salvar vidas.</p>\\r\\n<p>Nos complace informar de que 716 pacientes, incluidos niños, mujeres embarazadas, ancianos, recién nacidos y huérfanos, recibieron atención médica en la Clínica Médica SAI en el transcurso de los últimos tres meses. Nuestros servicios gratuitos han incluido exámenes físicos, electrocardiogramas, ecografías ginecológicas y obstétricas, controles de bienestar infantil, asesoramiento dietético y revisiones mensuales para mujeres embarazadas. Además, hemos podido proporcionar a nuestros pacientes medicamentos, vitaminas y suplementos nutricionales gratuitos.</p>\\r\\n<p>En SAI, nuestra pasión y misión es mejorar vidas. Le invitamos cordialmente a unirse a nosotros en la creación de un cambio genuino mediante donaciones regulares. Con su apoyo, podemos trabajar juntos para salvar vidas y ofrecer a los necesitados un futuro mejor.</p>\\r\\n<p>Hazte donante mensual y trabajemos por un futuro mejor para Venezuela. Muchas gracias.</p>\\r\\n\"}', '{\"en\": {\"seo_title\": \"SAI Medical Clinic 2023 Q2 Update!  Medical Clinic, SAI, health, Venezuela, health care, donation, free services\", \"seo_description\": \"Discover how the SAI Medical Clinic is transforming lives in 2023! From serving 716 patients to expanding care and offering free medicines, learn how your support brings hope to those in need.\", \"keywords\": \"SAI Venezuela, SAI Medical Clinic, free healthcare Venezuela, expanded waiting room, medical care for children, healthcare for pregnant women, free medical services Venezuela, community health programs, SAI donor impact, medical aid for elders, healthcare for orphans, Venezuela medical outreach, free medicine distribution, monthly donor for healthcare, Venezuela charity impact, SAI patient care.\", \"og_title\": \"SAI Medical Clinic 2023 Q2 Update!  Medical Clinic, SAI, health, Venezuela, health care, donation, free services\", \"og_description\": \"Discover how the SAI Medical Clinic is transforming lives in 2023! From serving 716 patients to expanding care and offering free medicines, learn how your support brings hope to those in need.\"}, \"es\": {\"seo_title\": \"Clínica SAI: 716 Pacientes Atendidos con Medicina Gratis y Cuidado Ampliado en Venezuela | 2023\", \"seo_description\": \"La Clínica SAI ha atendido a 716 pacientes en Venezuela, ofreciendo servicios médicos gratuitos y medicinas. Descubre cómo estamos transformando vidas y únete a nuestra causa.\", \"keywords\": null, \"og_title\": \"Clínica SAI: 716 Pacientes Atendidos con Medicina Gratis y Cuidado Ampliado en Venezuela | 2023\", \"og_description\": \"La Clínica SAI ha atendido a 716 pacientes en Venezuela, ofreciendo servicios médicos gratuitos y medicinas. Descubre cómo estamos transformando vidas y únete a nuestra causa.\"}}', 'published', 18, '2025-08-13 23:32:43', 1, 1, NULL, '2025-08-16 22:29:49'),
