&G Sanctuary: We provided 108 bags of dog food, weighing 5,940 pounds, to support the dogs in our sanctuary.</p>\\r\\n<p>Partner Shelters: Our collaboration with partner shelters enabled us to donate 97 bags of dog food, weighing 5,335 pounds, to support dogs across the country.</p>\\r\\n<p>Total: We provided a total of 205 bags of dog food, weighing 11,275 pounds, in the third quarter.</p>\\r\\n<p>Fourth Quarter Report (October-December)</p>\\r\\n<p>In the fourth quarter of 2024, we continued our efforts to support animal welfare in Venezuela. Key highlights include:</p>\\r\\n<p>SAI-A&G Sanctuary: We provided 144 bags of dog food, weighing 7,920 pounds, to support the dogs in our sanctuary.</p>\\r\\n<p>Partner Shelters: We donated another 97 bags of dog food, weighing 5,335 pounds, to support dogs across the country.</p>\\r\\n<p>Total: We provided a total of 241 bags of dog food, weighing 13,255 pounds, in the fourth quarter.</p>\\r\\n<p>As we continue to provide a safe haven for 130 deserving dogs, we rely on the generosity of our donors to ensure their well-being. Your ongoing support enables us to deliver essential care, nutritious food, and a loving environment, giving these dogs a second chance at a happy life. Together, we can make a lasting difference in the lives of these vulnerable companions.</p>\\r\\n\", \"es\": \"<h1>Patas de Esperanza: Cómo Tu Apoyo Alimentó y Salvó a Cientos de Perros en Venezuela en 2024</h1>\\r\\n<p>Al reflexionar sobre la segunda mitad de 2024, estamos orgullosos de compartir los logros de nuestro programa de bienestar animal en Venezuela. Este informe destaca nuestros principales avances e hitos de julio a diciembre de 2024, mostrando nuestro compromiso por mejorar la vida de los perros que más lo necesitan.</p>\\r\\n<p>Informe del Tercer Trimestre (julio - septiembre)</p>\\r\\n<p>En el tercer trimestre de 2024, logramos avances significativos en el apoyo al bienestar animal en Venezuela. Los aspectos más destacados incluyen:</p>\