i tation ullamcorper suscipit lobortis nis ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis autem vel eum iriure dolor in hendrerit in vulputate velit esse molestie consequat, vel illum dolore eu feugiat nulla facilisis at vero eros et accumsan et iusto odio dignissim. Qui blandit praesent luptatum zzril delenit augue duis dolore te feugait nulla\", \"donate_title\": \"Help people in need\", \"donate_text\": \"START DONATING TODAY, MAKE THE DIFFERENCE\", \"donate_button\": \"\"}, \"es\": {\"h1_title\": \"¡Salvando vidas de animales del zoológico!\", \"posted_by\": \"\", \"h3_1\": \"\", \"paragraph_1\": \"\", \"paragraph_2\": \"\", \"h3_2\": \"\", \"paragraph_3\": \"\", \"donate_title\": \"\", \"donate_text\": \"\", \"donate_button\": \"\"}}', '{\"en\": \"<h1>Saving Zoo Animals Lives in Venezuela!﻿</h1><br>\\r\\n<p>SAI brings more food and care for Animals</p>\\r\\n<p>Our Organization continues to work to save starving animals.</p>\\r\\n<p>To all our SAI and GlobalGiving donors, the SAI team is actively working with zoos and refuges that need our help. We have distributed 2,471 lbs of food in the past 5 months consisting of fruits, vegetables, and seeds to ensure all animals are properly fed. Food supplies include: papaya, bananas, plantain, watermelon, sunflowers seeds, eggs, proteins, dog food, vegetables, seeds, and milk. We also provided medication for the animals. We are currently caring for more than 40 different species of animals.</p>\\r\\n<p><strong>To all our SAI and GlobalGiving donors, the SAI team is actively working with zoos and refuges that need our help. We have distributed 2,471 lbs of food in the past 5 months consisting of fruits, vegetables, and seeds to ensure all animals are properly fed. Food supplies include: papaya, bananas, plantain, watermelon, sunflowers seeds, eggs, proteins, dog food, vegetables, seeds, and milk. We also provided medication for the animals. We are currently caring for more than 40 different species of animals.</strong></p>\\r\\n<p>Our program provides essential food and medical care for zoo animals that currently reside in one zoo and two animal refuges in Venezuela. SAI is rescuing animals at risk of starvation with its partners. Our commitment will always be to save and care for animals in that they can be happy, well nourished, and healthy.</p>\\r\\n\", \"es\": \"<h1>¡Salvando vidas de animales del zoológico!</h1>\\r\\n<p>SAI trae más alimento y cuidado para los Animales</p>\\r\\n<p>Nuestra Organización sigue trabajando para salvar animales hambrientos en los zoologicos de Venezuela. A todos nuestros donantes de SAI y GlobalGiving, el equipo de SAI está trabajando activamente con zoológicos y refugios que necesitan nuestra ayuda. Hemos distribuido 2,471 libras de alimentos en los últimos 5 meses que consisten en frutas, verduras y semillas para garantizar que todos los animales estén alimentados adecuadamente. Los suministros de alimentos incluyen: papaya, plátano, sandía, semillas de girasol, huevos, proteínas, comida para perros, verduras y leche. También proporcionamos medicamentos para los animales. Actualmente cuidamos a más de 40 especies diferentes de animales.</p>\\r\\n<p>Nuestro programa brinda atención médica y alimentos esenciales para los animales del zoológico que actualmente residen en un zoológico y dos refugios de animales en Venezuela. SAI está rescatando animales en riesgo de morir de hambre. Nuestro compromiso siempre será salvar y cuidar a los animales para que esten siempre felices, bien alimentados y saludables.</p>\\r\\n\"}', '{\"en\": {\"seo_title\": \"SAI Venezuela Distributes 2,471 lbs of Food to Starving Animals - Rescue Update 2023\", \"seo_description\": \"In the past 5 months, SAI Venezuela provided 2,471 lbs of food and medical care to 40+ endangered species in Venezuelan zoos and refuges. Support our rescue mission today.\", \"keywords\": \"SAI Venezuela, animal rescue Venezuela, starving animals Venezuela, zoo animals Venezuela, Venezuelan wildlife rescue, animal food donations, wildlife conservation Venezuela, endangered species Venezuela, animal refuge support, GlobalGiving Venezuela, animal medication Venezuela, SAI animal program\", \"og_title\": \"SAI Venezuela Distributes 2,471 lbs of Food to Starving Animals - Rescue Update 2023\", \"og_description\": \"In the past 5 months, SAI Venezuela provided 2,471 lbs of food and medical care to 40+ endangered species in Venezuelan zoos and refuges. Support our rescue mission today.\"}, \"es\": {\"seo_title\": \"¡Salvando vidas de animales del zoológico!\", \"seo_description\": \"¡Salvando vidas de animales del zoológico!\", \"keywords\": null, \"og_title\": \"¡Salvando vidas de animales del zoológico!\", \"og_description\": \"¡Salvando vidas de animales del zoológico!\"}}', 'published', 1, '2025-08-14 01:30:37', 1, 1, NULL, '2025-08-14 23:59:21'),
