rci tation ullamcorper suscipit lobortis nis ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis autem vel eum iriure dolor in hendrerit in vulputate velit esse molestie consequat, vel illum dolore eu feugiat nulla facilisis at vero eros et accumsan et iusto odio dignissim. Qui blandit praesent luptatum zzril delenit augue duis dolore te feugait nulla\", \"donate_title\": \"Help people in need\", \"donate_text\": \"START DONATING TODAY, MAKE THE DIFFERENCE\", \"donate_button\": \"\"}, \"es\": {\"h1_title\": \"Entregas de comida a los zoológicos\", \"posted_by\": \"\", \"h3_1\": \"\", \"paragraph_1\": \"\", \"paragraph_2\": \"\", \"h3_2\": \"\", \"paragraph_3\": \"\", \"donate_title\": \"\", \"donate_text\": \"\", \"donate_button\": \"\"}}', '{\"en\": \"<h1>Food Deliveries to the Zoos in Venezuela</h1><br>\\r\\n<p>Food Deliveries to the Zoos</p>\\r\\n<p>SAI staff continuously works closely with partners to rescue and care for injured and sick wild animals. In August, SAI partners rescued a hawk that was found injured. The hawk had a broken wing, it was taken to the facility and received the necessary treatment and medication. Presently, the hawk has been returned to its natural habitat in the forest.</p>\\r\\n<p>The SAI team is delivering food and medicine to zoos. The zoos receive fruits, vegetables, and meat.</p>\\r\\n<p>We have delivered over 1,810 pounds of food during the past three months:</p>\\r\\n<p>Food for Mice</p>\\r\\n<p>Green beans</p>\\r\\n<p>Sunflower seeds</p>\\r\\n\", \"es\": \"<h1>Entregas de comida a los zoológicos</h1>\\r\\n<p>El personal de SAI trabaja continuamente en estrecha colaboración con sus colaboradores para rescatar y cuidar a los animales salvajes que estan heridos y enfermos. En agosto, uno de nuestros colaboradores de SAI rescató un halcón que fue encontrado herido. El Halcón tenía un ala rota, fue trasladado al establecimiento de cuidados y recibió el tratamiento y medicación necesaria. Actualmente, el halcón ha sido devuelto a su hábitat natural en el bosque.</p>\\r\\n<p>El equipo de SAI está entregando alimentos y medicinas a los zoológicos. Los zoológicos reciben frutas, verduras y carne. Hemos entregado más de 1,810 libras de alimentos durante los últimos tres meses:</p>\\r\\n<p>Comida para ratones</p>\\r\\n<p>Judías verdes</p>\\r\\n<p>calabacines</p>\\r\\n<p>Semillas de girasol</p>\\r\\n<p>salvado de trigo</p>\\r\\n\"}', '{\"en\": {\"seo_title\": \"SAI Venezuela Rescues Injured Hawk, Delivers 1,810 lbs of Food to Zoos – Wildlife Update\", \"seo_description\": \"In the past 3 months, SAI Venezuela delivered 1,810 lbs of food to zoos and successfully rehabilitated an injured hawk. Join our mission to protect Venezuela’s wildlife.\", \"keywords\": \"SAI Venezuela, wildlife rescue Venezuela, injured hawk rescue, Venezuelan zoo support, animal rehabilitation Venezuela, wildlife conservation, animal food donations, bird rescue Venezuela, zoo animal care, SAI animal partners, wildlife medicine Venezuela\", \"og_title\": \"SAI Venezuela Rescues Injured Hawk, Delivers 1,810 lbs of Food to Zoos – Wildlife Update\", \"og_description\": \"In the past 3 months, SAI Venezuela delivered 1,810 lbs of food to zoos and successfully rehabilitated an injured hawk. Join our mission to protect Venezuela’s wildlife.\"}, \"es\": {\"seo_title\": \"Entregas de comida a los zoológicos\", \"seo_description\": \"Entregas de comida a los zoológicos\", \"keywords\": null, \"og_title\": \"Entregas de comida a los zoológicos\", \"og_description\": \"Entregas de comida a los zoológicos\"}}', 'published', 0, '2025-08-14 01:30:37', 1, 1, NULL, '2025-08-14 01:30:37');
