ico. Nuestro meta es proteger y preservar todas las especies de animales en Venezuela.</p>\\r\\n<p>En el Q3 2022, nuestro equipo distribuyó 2,685 libras de comida incluyendo entre ellas: bananas, huevos, semillas, papaya, girasoles, carne, avena, frijoles,calabaza, proteina, mango, sandia, leche en polvo, zanahoria, maiz, tómates y más.</p>\\r\\n<p>Estamos haciendo la diferencia, gracias por tu apoyo, para que continuemos salvando animales juntos.</p>\\r\\n\"}', '{\"en\": {\"seo_title\": \"SAI-A&G Venezuela Rescues Turtles & Hedgehog, Distributes 2,685 lbs of Food – Q3 2022 Impact Report\", \"seo_description\": \"In Q3 2022, SAI-A&G Venezuela distributed 2,685 lbs of food to animals in need and rescued a turtle family & baby hedgehog. Support wildlife conservation in Venezuela today!\", \"keywords\": \"SAI-A&G Venezuela, animal rescue Venezuela, endangered species Venezuela, Venezuelan wildlife conservation, zoo donations Venezuela, turtle rescue Venezuela, African hedgehog rescue, animal food supply Venezuela, wildlife protection Venezuela, SAI-A&G animal program\", \"og_title\": \"SAI-A&G Venezuela Rescues Turtles & Hedgehog, Distributes 2,685 lbs of Food – Q3 2022 Impact Report\", \"og_description\": \"In Q3 2022, SAI-A&G Venezuela distributed 2,685 lbs of food to animals in need and rescued a turtle family & baby hedgehog. Support wildlife conservation in Venezuela today!\"}, \"es\": {\"seo_title\": \"Programa de rescate animal de SAI-A&G\", \"seo_description\": \"Programa de rescate animal de SAI-A&G\", \"keywords\": null, \"og_title\": \"Programa de rescate animal de SAI-A&G\", \"og_description\": \"Programa de rescate animal de SAI-A&G\"}}', 'published', 0, '2025-08-14 01:30:37', 1, 1, NULL, '2025-08-14 01:30:37'),
